@startuml
actor User
participant "ClassroomAI System" as System
participant "Google 驗證服務" as Google

User -> System : 開啟 Line 頁面
User -> System : 加入 Line Bot

System -> Google : 導向 Google 登入
Google -> User : 輸入帳號密碼
User -> Google : 提交帳號密碼

Google -> System : 驗證成功並回傳 Token
System -> System : 驗證 Token
System -> System : 綁定帳號
System -> User : 登入成功訊息

@enduml
